body_html:
As your logs show, the error is thrown due to a missing function call in psutil library.
https://github.com/giampaolo/psutil/blob/master/HISTORY.rst#200

cpu_count seems to be added in version 2.0.0 of psutil.
So running the following command should fix your problem:

sudo pip install --upgrade psutil

Also the stacktrace shows that this is a call in dask library. So this issue is better reported to dask library.

body:
As your logs show, the error is thrown due to a missing function call in psutil library.
https://github.com/giampaolo/psutil/blob/master/HISTORY.rst#200

cpu_count seems to be added in version 2.0.0 of psutil.
So running the following command should fix your problem:
```
sudo pip install --upgrade psutil
```
Also the stacktrace shows that this is a call in `dask` library. So this issue is better reported to dask library.
